{"tid":114791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星航美女空姐暴斃惹風波　網民稱請病假影響晉升","createTime":"2017-02-10T05:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T10:32:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0357b56b4d660803737a84e7811d8168cfee9d9","tid":114791,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/bknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fbknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001.html&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6e65723f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/bknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/photo/bknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001_01b.jpg&h=14e3981f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡航空公司一名空姐，上周三在從美國三藩市返回新加坡的航班起飛前數個小時，被發現倒斃在酒店客房內，事件引起熱烈討論。有人近日在網上直指星航刻薄員工，更暗中訂下罰則，請病假的員工會影響晉升機會，令一眾員工帶病也要「頂硬上」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170209/photo/bknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170209%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170209114649997-0209_17011_001_02b.jpg&h=2d6ea4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n38歲的雲妮莎‧葉（Vanessa Yeap，音譯）上周三逝世，有指她曾向同事透露身體不適。一名網名菲利普‧林（Philip Lim）的人在個人facebook聲稱，星航的員工都不會請病假，因為這會影響晉升機會。他又指每一名員工都會有10分底分，若然員工全年請超過12天病假，便會全數被扣掉。請病假的次數更會成為晉升的評核準則之一，約佔分數的4至6%。而全年沒有請病假的員工，會獲得公司額外獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n星航方面否認有關說法，指出不會因為員工沒有請病假而給予額外獎勵，若然員工因病請假，便應在家中好好休息，如員工因患上嚴重疾病，公司還會給予額外的有薪假期。"},{"pid":"8fa2cbbdda826c4a5f60fbe4f3dd6103953744ed","tid":114791,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"我有冇眼花？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美女？"},{"pid":"111d30f38d7d73bc10bf93f9fd4433d71b37eead","tid":114791,"uid":6721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有冇眼花？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美女？</blockquote><br />\n呢隻樣喺鬼佬眼中係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e1816e5574638173aa0436a66b927f1c8d0b4b","tid":114791,"uid":33241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有冇眼花？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美女？</blockquote><br />\n呢隻樣喺鬼佬眼中係靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7b06361fcf7fe2a767ddbcaf158c1224431b5f","tid":114791,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69dcf22eefd646673aec4a213463d9cabac54116","tid":114791,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"美女外表特徵，佢全部都冇"},{"pid":"aeb9a7d9cc3802bfed96b5a7839601d8f471bf77","tid":114791,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"坡豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}